  "theme": {
    "name": "Theme System",
    "description": "All tools share the Vesper color palette via a centralized theme system. Colors are defined once in vesper.sh and propagated to Ghostty, Warp, Cursor, Yazi, btop, lsd, and fzf through template generation.\n",
